| z0_col9  | int(11) | YES  |     | (`z0_col0` * 8) | VIRTUAL GENERATED |
| z0_col16 | int(11) | YES  |     | (`z0_col1` * 7) | STORED GENERATED  |
| z0_col17 | int(11) | YES  |     | (`z0_col1` * 8) | STORED GENERATED  |
