|       6 |       0 |       6 |       0 | 60      | 6       |
|      11 |       1 |      12 |      11 | 111     | 11      |
|      12 |       2 |      14 |      24 | 122     | 12      |
|      13 |       3 |      16 |      39 | 133     | 13      |
+---------+---------+---------+---------+---------+---------+
desc test_table2;//
+---------+--------------+------+-----+-----------------------------+-------------------+
| Field   | Type         | Null | Key | Default                     | Extra             |
+---------+--------------+------+-----+-----------------------------+-------------------+
| z0_col0 | int(11)      | NO   | PRI | NULL                        |                   |
| z0_col1 | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL                        |                   |
| z0_col2 | int(11)      | YES  |     | (`z0_col0` + `z0_col1`)     | VIRTUAL GENERATED |
| z0_col3 | int(11)      | YES  |     | (`z0_col0` * `z0_col1`)     | STORED GENERATED  |
| z0_col4 | varchar(100) | YES  |     | concat(`z0_col0`,`z0_col1`) | VIRTUAL GENERATED |
| z0_col5 | varchar(100) | YES  |     | `z0_col0`                   | STORED GENERATED  |
